{%- comment -%}
  Global typography system for the Sneakies site — Home Page AND the entire
  Claim Flow both render this once, near the top of their own {%- style -%}
  block, so every component inherits from the same three tokens instead of
  hardcoding a font-family on individual elements:

  - --font-display : Azo Super Uber       — hero/section headlines, product &
                       flavor names, ingredient titles, confirmation/offer
                       headings, large marketing copy.
  - --font-heading  : Stenciletta Solid Bold — subtitles, nav labels, button
                       text, badges, pills, card titles, form section
                       headings, highlighted info.
  - --font-body     : Gimlet Sans Variable   — paragraphs, descriptions,
                       footer text, form labels/helper/placeholder text,
                       inputs, small informational copy.

  Only one @font-face block per typeface is declared no matter how many times
  this snippet is rendered on a page, since browsers de-dupe identical
  @font-face rules by (font-family, src, weight, style) — safe even though
  both sneakies-landing.liquid and sneakies-claim.liquid render it.
{%- endcomment -%}
@font-face{
  font-family:'Azo Super Uber';
  src:url({{ 'AzoSuperUber.woff2' | asset_url }}) format('woff2'),
      url({{ 'AzoSuperUber.woff' | asset_url }}) format('woff');
  font-weight:400;
  font-style:normal;
  font-display:swap;
}
@font-face{
  font-family:'Stenciletta Solid Bold';
  src:url({{ 'StencilettaSolidBold.woff2' | asset_url }}) format('woff2'),
      url({{ 'StencilettaSolidBold.woff' | asset_url }}) format('woff');
  font-weight:700;
  font-style:normal;
  font-display:swap;
}
@font-face{
  font-family:'Gimlet Sans Variable';
  src:url({{ 'GimletSansVariable.woff2' | asset_url }}) format('woff2'),
      url({{ 'GimletSansVariable.woff' | asset_url }}) format('woff');
  font-weight:300 900;
  font-style:normal;
  font-display:swap;
}
@font-face{
  font-family:'Gimlet Sans Variable';
  src:url({{ 'GimletSansVariable.woff2' | asset_url }}) format('woff2'),
      url({{ 'GimletSansVariable.woff' | asset_url }}) format('woff');
  font-weight:300 900;
  font-style:italic;
  font-display:swap;
}
:root{
  --font-display:'Azo Super Uber', Impact, 'Arial Narrow', sans-serif;
  --font-heading:'Stenciletta Solid Bold', 'Archivo Narrow', sans-serif;
  --font-body:'Gimlet Sans Variable', 'Archivo', system-ui, sans-serif;
}
